    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that won't break the bank? This car is in fair condition and shows some honest signs of its time on the road, but it remains a solid performer that\u2019s ready for your daily commute! It runs well and offers great value for anyone seeking reliable transportation with a bit of character. Come see why this practical choice is perfect for your next adventure!",
