    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for those seeking a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several medium-sized dents and some fading in the paint, while the interior has noticeable wear on the upholstery and some minor staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may require some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak operating shape. It is a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes reliability over aesthetics.",
