    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector's dream. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. Every feature works exactly as it did the day it left the factory, making this a rare find for any serious buyer.",
      "price": 49500.0,
